    <title><![CDATA[常用的Markdown语法]]></title>
    <link href="http://lufeiblog.github.io/2014/10/14/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%94%A8%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9Bmarkdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/"/>
    <id>http://lufeiblog.github.io/2014/10/14/博客用到的一些markdown语法/</id>
    <published>2014-10-14T05:59:54.000Z</published>
    <updated>2014-10-14T06:00:12.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这是写博客平时经常用到的一些markdown的语法…</p>
<h2 id="Markdown的一些语法">Markdown的一些语法</h2>
<h3 id="1-html代码可以直接解释:">1.html代码可以直接解释:</h3>
<p>在markdown中，markdown支持html标签，md文件解析为html时原有的html部分会保留。有基于此，我们只要在文中插入符合html规范的代码即可。</p>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">div</span> <span class="attribute">style</span>=<span class="value">"width:100px;height:100px;background:black"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">div</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<p><div style="width:100px;height:100px;background:black"></div></p>
<h3 id="2-博客目录:">2.博客目录:</h3>
<p>自动截取markdown中的#号标题,并进行渲染成目录</p>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">[TOC]</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<p><img src="/img/codeyanshi2.png" alt=""></p>
<h3 id="3-列表:">3.列表:</h3>
<p>无序列表:</p>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>red</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>blue</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>green</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<ul>
<li>red</li>
<li>blue</li>
<li>green</li>
</ul>
<p>有序列表:</p>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>apple</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>banana</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">3. </span>cate</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<ol>
<li>apple</li>
<li>banana</li>
<li>cate</li>
</ol>
<p>嵌套列表:</p>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">+ bullet list 1</div><div class="line">   -<span class="ruby"> sub item <span class="number">1</span></span></div><div class="line">   -<span class="ruby"> sub item <span class="number">2</span></span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<ul>
<li>bullet list 2<ul>
<li>sub item 1 </li>
<li>sub item 2</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="4-引用区块:">4.引用区块:</h3>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&gt; <span class="keyword">this</span> <span class="keyword">is</span> a book</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>this is a book</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="5-字体:">5.字体:</h3>
<p>斜体:</p>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">*</span>斜体字<span class="keyword">*</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<p><em>斜体字</em></p>
<p>粗体:</p>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">*</span><span class="keyword">*</span>粗体字<span class="keyword">*</span><span class="keyword">*</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<p><strong>粗体字</strong></p>
<h3 id="6-特殊数学表达式:">6.特殊数学表达式:</h3>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">![](http:<span class="comment">//latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?latex公式)</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<p><img src="http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?{\sqrt{2\pi}}" alt=""></p>
<h3 id="7-文本链接:">7.文本链接:</h3>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">[<span class="link_label">baidu</span>](<span class="link_url">http://www.baidu.com</span>)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<p><a href="http://www.baidu.com" target="_blank" rel="external">baidu</a></p>
<h3 id="8-标题:">8.标题:</h3>
<p>文字前面加几个#号</p>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="preprocessor">## Quick Start</span></div><div class="line"><span class="preprocessor">### Create a new post</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<p>看标题即可</p>
<h3 id="9-代码:">9.代码:</h3>
<p>嵌入文本的代码:</p>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">我是文本中<span class="code">`代码块`</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<p>我是文本中<code>代码块</code></p>
<p>一大段的代码:</p>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span></span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">switch</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<pre><code><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span></span>
<span class="keyword">if</span>
<span class="keyword">while</span>
<span class="keyword">for</span>
<span class="keyword">switch</span>
</code></pre><h3 id="10-高光代码:">10.高光代码:</h3>
<p>代码:</p>
<p><img src="/img/codeyanshi1.png" alt=""></p>
<p><br>效果:</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"My New Post"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br></p>
<figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">'hello world'</span>;</div><div class="line">print_r(<span class="string">'hello world'</span>);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="11-插入网页元素(图像、音频、视频）:">11.插入网页元素(图像、音频、视频）:</h3>
<p>插入图像:</p>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">![](http:<span class="comment">//ww2.sinaimg.cn/large/5e8cb366jw1e62o63tkv3j20dh078q5a.jpg)</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<p><img src="http://ww2.sinaimg.cn/large/5e8cb366jw1e62o63tkv3j20dh078q5a.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p>插入音乐:</p>
<p>某些网站歌曲页面有个『转帖』选项，将html代码或javascript代码复制到文中即可。</p>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;embed <span class="variable">src=</span><span class="string">"http://www.xiami.com/widget/0_3515679/singlePlayer.swf"</span> <span class="variable">type=</span><span class="string">"application/x-shockwave-flash"</span> <span class="variable">width=</span><span class="string">"257"</span> <span class="variable">height=</span><span class="string">"33"</span> <span class="variable">wmode=</span><span class="string">"transparent"</span>&gt;&lt;/embed&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<embed src="http://www.xiami.com/widget/0_3515679/singlePlayer.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="257" height="33" wmode="transparent">

<p>插入视频:</p>
<p>嵌入视频的方法和音乐类似，视频网站每个视频页面都会有一个『分享』或『转帖』按钮，点击可以查看代码。</p>
<p>代码:</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">iframe</span> <span class="attribute">height</span>=<span class="value">498</span> <span class="attribute">width</span>=<span class="value">510</span> <span class="attribute">src</span>=<span class="value">"http://player.youku.com/embed/XMjI2MjU3MDMy"</span> <span class="attribute">frameborder</span>=<span class="value">0</span> <span class="attribute">allowfullscreen</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">iframe</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><br>效果:</p>
<embed src="http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNjM0MjI1NTI4/v.swf" allowfullscreen="true" quality="high" width="700" height="400" align="middle" allowscriptaccess="always" type="application/x-shockwave-flash">]]></content>
